data.description: Experience serene living in this charming 3BR, 3BA, tri-level home nestled on 2.53 acres of tranquil beauty! Inside you will find: a Kitchen with plentiful cabinet space; lengthy dining room boasting lots of natural light; Formal living room and additional dining area/office; Spacious Den w/cozy stone Wood-burning FP (has gas line that has been capped) and exterior access to large patio; Flex room-great for workout room or storage! Primary BR w/balcony, perfect for your morning coffee. Outside, experience peaceful living on the sprawling, level 2.53 acres, graced by an enchanting 1800s cabin and two waterfall ponds. Pole barn complete with a stacked stone fireplace is a perfect spot for gatherings year-round. Two driveways-one at the front & back - offer ample parking for toys or guests.
